description: Product Description PAUL & JOE "it's about having fun.I don't ask for advice, I just have things I love." Sophie Mechaly Paul & Joe's vision of a woman is that of a "selfish and charming adult woman". A stylish woman with a strong will and conviction that is so strong that it seems selfish, and who clearly knows what she wants. BEAUTE CONCEPT Cosmetics that offer the Parisienne lifestyle of thoroughly enjoying life Not only do they enhance your appearance, but they also bring joy through their visual appeal, tactile sensation, decorative charm, and the happiness of owning them. Paul & Joe Beauté promotes a lifestyle that fills not only yourself but also those around you with a sense of happiness. PRODUCT The skin that Paul & Joe aims for is "radiant and glowing from within" Even if the look is glamorous, the focus is on achieving a natural finish where the person’s presence shines more than the colours of the makeup. Carefully selected floral treatment ingredients are blended effectively to spread comfortably over the skin, leading to soft, radiant skin that glows from the inside. DESIGN Retro-modern The packaging, exuding refined luxury and sophisticated shine, is perfect for mature women. Each product has a unique presence, brimming with the power to fill your dressing table with an air of happiness.
